paragraphs.text:
%md
## Corona-analysis

Some basic analysis of the coronavirus...

### Data Sources

* **CSSE COVID-19 Dataset**:
    * https://github.com/CSSEGISandData/COVID-19/tree/master/csse_covid_19_data
* **HDX - Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19) Cases Data**:
    * https://data.humdata.org/dataset/novel-coronavirus-2019-ncov-cases
* **Ministerio de Sanidad**:
    * https://www.mscbs.gob.es/profesionales/saludPublica/ccayes/alertasActual/nCov-China/situacionActual.htm

### Pre-requisites
* Set "zeppelin.shell.interpolation" to "true" in the shell interpreter config.
* Set "zeppelin.spark.maxResult" to "5000" in the Spark interpreter config.
* Enable the "zeppelin-number" visualization in Helium.

paragraphs.title: Summary
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select
    Country_Region as Country,
    sum(Confirmed) as Confirmed,
    sum(Deaths) as Deaths,
    sum(Recovered) as Recovered,
    sum(Active) as Active,
    (sum(Deaths) / sum(Confirmed) * 100 ) as DeathRatioPerConfirmed,
    (sum(Deaths) / (sum(Recovered) + sum(Deaths)) * 100 ) as DeathRatioPerClosed
from coronareport
group by Country
order by 2 desc

paragraphs.title: Data preparation
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._

val dfConfirmed = spark.read
    .options(Map("inferSchema"->"true","header"->"true"))
    .csv("time_series_covid19_confirmed_global_narrow.csv")
    .withColumnRenamed("Province/State", "State")
    .withColumnRenamed("Country/Region", "Country")
    .withColumn("Date", col("Date").cast(DateType))
    .withColumn("Value", col("Value").cast(IntegerType))

val dfDeaths = spark.read
    .options(Map("inferSchema"->"true","header"->"true"))
    .csv("time_series_covid19_deaths_global_narrow.csv")
    .withColumnRenamed("Province/State", "State")
    .withColumnRenamed("Country/Region", "Country")
    .withColumn("Date", col("Date").cast(DateType))
    .withColumn("Value", col("Value").cast(IntegerType))
    
val dfRecovered = spark.read
    .options(Map("inferSchema"->"true","header"->"true"))
    .csv("time_series_covid19_recovered_global_narrow.csv")
    .withColumnRenamed("Province/State", "State")
    .withColumnRenamed("Country/Region", "Country")
    .withColumn("Date", col("Date").cast(DateType))
    .withColumn("Value", col("Value").cast(IntegerType))
    
println("Record count (confirmed): " + dfConfirmed.count)
dfConfirmed.printSchema()
dfConfirmed.show(5)

println("Record count (confirmed): " + dfDeaths.count)
dfDeaths.printSchema()
dfDeaths.show(5)

println("Record count (confirmed): " + dfRecovered.count)
dfRecovered.printSchema()
dfRecovered.show(5)

dfConfirmed.registerTempTable("confirmed_timeseries")
dfDeaths.registerTempTable("deaths_timeseries")
dfRecovered.registerTempTable("recovered_timeseries")

paragraphs.title: Daily cases (WorldWide)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select today.Date, (today.Value - yesterday.Value) as new_cases
from (
  select date_add(Date, 1) as Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from confirmed_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as yesterday, 
(
  select Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from confirmed_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as today
where yesterday.Date = today.Date
  and today.Date > '2020-02-01'
order by today.Date

paragraphs.title: Daily increase percentage (Worldwide)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select today.Date, ((today.Value / yesterday.Value) - 1) * 100 as daily_increase_pct
from (
  select date_add(Date, 1) as Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from confirmed_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as yesterday, 
(
  select Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from confirmed_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as today
where yesterday.Date = today.Date
  and today.Date > '2020-02-01'
order by today.Date

paragraphs.title: Evolution (Main Countries)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select Country, Date, Value
from deaths_timeseries
where Country in ("Spain", "Italy", "Germany", "France", "US", "United Kingdom")
  and Date > '2020-02-15'
order by Date

paragraphs.title: Daily deaths (Worldwide)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select today.Date, (today.Value - yesterday.Value) as new_deaths
from (
  select date_add(Date, 1) as Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from deaths_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as yesterday, 
(
  select Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from deaths_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as today
where yesterday.Date = today.Date
  and today.Date > '2020-02-01'
order by today.Date

paragraphs.title: Daily deaths increase percentage (Worldwide)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select today.Date, ((today.Value / yesterday.Value) - 1) * 100 as new_deaths_incr
from (
  select date_add(Date, 1) as Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from deaths_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as yesterday, 
(
  select Date, sum(Value) as Value
  from deaths_timeseries
--  where Country = "Spain"
  group by Date
) as today
where yesterday.Date = today.Date
  and today.Date > '2020-02-01'
order by today.Date

paragraphs.title: Evolution
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select Country, Date, Value
from recovered_timeseries
where Country in ("Spain", "Italy", "Germany", "France", "US", "United Kingdom")
  and Date > '2020-02-15'
order by Date

paragraphs.title: Daily cases
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select today.Date, (today.Value - yesterday.Value) as new_recovered
from (
  select date_add(Date, 1) as Date, Value
  from recovered_timeseries
  where Country = "Spain"
) as yesterday, 
(
  select Date, Value
  from recovered_timeseries
  where Country = "Spain"
) as today
where yesterday.Date = today.Date
  and today.Date > '2020-02-15'
order by today.Date

  from recovered_timeseries

  select Date, Value
  from recovered_timeseries
  where Country = "Spain"
) as today
where yesterday.Date = today.Date
  and today.Date > '2020-03-15'
order by today.Date

paragraphs.text:
%md
# Generic time series analysis

paragraphs.title: Worldwide evolution (incl. active)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select cts.Date,
       confirmed,
       recovered,
       deaths,
       (confirmed - (recovered + deaths)) as active
from (
   select Date, sum(Value) as confirmed
   from confirmed_timeseries
   group by Date
) as cts,
(
   select Date, sum(Value) as recovered
   from recovered_timeseries
   group by Date
) as  rts,
(
   select Date, sum(Value) as deaths
   from deaths_timeseries
   group by Date
) as dts 
where 1 = 1
  and cts.Date = rts.Date
  and rts.Date = dts.Date
  and cts.Date > '2020-02-01'
order by cts.Date

paragraphs.title: Spain evolution (incl. active)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select cts.Country, cts.Date,
       cts.Value as confirmed,
       rts.Value as recovered,
       dts.Value as deaths,
       (cts.Value - (rts.Value + dts.Value)) as active
from confirmed_timeseries cts, recovered_timeseries rts, deaths_timeseries dts 
where cts.Country in ("Spain") and rts.Country in ("Spain") and dts.Country in ("Spain")
  and cts.Date = rts.Date
  and rts.Date = dts.Date
  and cts.Date > '2020-02-15'
order by Date

paragraphs.title: Spain daily deaths increase (breakdown)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select cts.Country,
       cts.Date,
       dts.Value / cts.Value * 100 as deathsPerConfirmed,
       dts.Value / (rts.Value + dts.Value) * 100 as deathsPerClosed
from confirmed_timeseries cts, recovered_timeseries rts, deaths_timeseries dts 
where cts.Country in ("Spain") and rts.Country in ("Spain") and dts.Country in ("Spain")
  and cts.Date = rts.Date
  and rts.Date = dts.Date
  and cts.Date > '2020-02-15'
order by cts.Date

paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.to_date
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.udf

// *********************
// CCAA TIME SERIES LOAD
// *********************
val df = spark.read
    .options(Map("inferSchema"->"true","header"->"true"))
    .csv("serie_historica_acumulados.csv")
    .withColumnRenamed("PCR+", "PCR")
    .withColumnRenamed("TestAc+", "TestAc")
    .withColumn("Fecha", to_date($"Fecha", "dd/MM/yyyy"))

println("Record count: " + df.count)
df.printSchema()
df.show(5)

df.registerTempTable("ccaa_timeseries")

val dfContryCodes = spark.read
    .options(Map("inferSchema"->"true", "header"->"true"))
    .csv("IP2LOCATION-ISO3166-2.CSV")

println("Record count: " + dfContryCodes.count)
dfContryCodes.printSchema()
dfContryCodes.show(5)

dfContryCodes.registerTempTable("ccaa_iso_codes")

println("Last date loaded...")
df.agg(max("Fecha")).show()

// *************************
// CCAA MAPPING TO ISO CODES
// *************************
val ccaaMappingDf = Seq(
    ("Andalucía","ES-AN"),
    ("Aragón","ES-AR"),
    ("Asturias, Principado de","ES-AS"),
    ("Canarias","ES-CN"),
    ("Cantabria","ES-CB"),
    ("Castilla y León","ES-CL"),
    ("Castilla - La Mancha","ES-CM"),
    ("Cataluña","ES-CT"),
    ("Ceuta","ES-CE"),
    ("Extremadura","ES-EX"),
    ("Galicia","ES-GA"),
    ("Balears, Illes","ES-IB"),
    ("Rioja, La","ES-RI"),
    ("Madrid, Comunidad de","ES-MD"),
    ("Melilla","ES-ML"),
    ("Murcia, Región de","ES-MC"),
    ("Navarra, Comunidad Foral de","ES-NC"),
    ("País Vasco","ES-PV"),
    ("Comunitat Valenciana","ES-VC")
).toDF("name", "iso_code")

println("Record count: " + ccaaMappingDf.count)
ccaaMappingDf.printSchema()
ccaaMappingDf.show(10)

ccaaMappingDf.registerTempTable("ccaa_iso_codes_mapping")

// ***************
// CCAA DEMOGRAPHY
// ***************
// Remove dots from numbers in order to convert to Integer
val replaceDots: String => String = _.replaceAll("\\.", "")
val replaceDotsUDF = udf(replaceDots)

// Remove initial part of CCAA (e.g. "10 Comunidad Valenciana" --> "Comunidad Valenciana")
val renameCCAA: String => String = _.substring(3)
val renameCCAAUDF = udf(renameCCAA)


val dfCCAA = spark.read
    .options(Map("delimiter"->";", "inferSchema"->"true", "header" -> "true"))
    .csv("ccaa_demography_ine.csv")
    .withColumnRenamed("Comunidades y Ciudades Autónomas", "CCAA")
    .withColumn("CCAA", renameCCAAUDF(col("CCAA")))
    .withColumn("Total", when(!col("Total").isNull, replaceDotsUDF(col("Total"))))
    .withColumn("Total", col("Total").cast(DataTypes.IntegerType))


println("Record count: " + dfCCAA.count)
dfCCAA.printSchema()
dfCCAA.show(10)

dfCCAA.registerTempTable("ccaa_demography")

paragraphs.title: Spain evolution (daily)
paragraphs.text:
%sql
select
    today.Fecha as Fecha,
    ((today.Casos + today.PCR) - (yesterday.Casos + yesterday.PCR)) as new_Casos,
    today.Fallecidos - yesterday.Fallecidos as new_Fallecidos
--    today.Recuperados - yesterday.Recuperados as new_Recuperados
from (
    select date_add(Fecha, 1) as Fecha,
        sum(Hospitalizados) as Hospitalizados,
        sum(UCI) as UCI,
        sum(Fallecidos) as Fallecidos,
--        sum(Recuperados) as Recuperados,
        sum(nvl(CASOS,0) + nvl(PCR,0)) as Casos,
--        sum((nvl(CASOS,0) + nvl(PCR,0)) - (Recuperados + Fallecidos)) as Activos,
        sum(PCR) as PCR,
        sum(TestAc) as TestAc
    from ccaa_timeseries
    group by Fecha
) as yesterday,
(
    select Fecha,
        sum(Hospitalizados) as Hospitalizados,
        sum(UCI) as UCI,
        sum(Fallecidos) as Fallecidos,
--        sum(Recuperados) as Recuperados,
        sum(nvl(CASOS,0) + nvl(PCR,0)) as Casos,
--        sum((nvl(CASOS,0) + nvl(PCR,0)) - (Recuperados + Fallecidos)) as Activos,
        sum(PCR) as PCR,
        sum(TestAc) as TestAc
    from ccaa_timeseries
    group by Fecha
) as today
where yesterday.Fecha = today.Fecha
order by today.Fecha

%sql
select *
from (
  select subdivision_name as Comunidad_Autonoma, ct.CCAA as Codigo_CCAA,
         Total as Poblacion, format_number(Total * 100 / (select sum(Total) from ccaa_demography where Periodo = "2019" and Sexo = "Total"), 2) as pct_Poblacion,
         (nvl(CASOS,0) + nvl(PCR,0)) as Casos, format_number( (nvl(CASOS,0) + nvl(PCR,0)) * 100 / (select sum(nvl(CASOS,0) + nvl(PCR,0)) from ccaa_timeseries where Fecha = m.ultima_fecha), 2) as pct_Casos,
         Fallecidos, format_number(Fallecidos * 100 / (select sum(Fallecidos) from ccaa_timeseries where Fecha = m.ultima_fecha), 2) as pct_Fallecidos,
--         Recuperados, format_number(Recuperados * 100 / (select sum(Recuperados) from ccaa_timeseries where Fecha = m.ultima_fecha), 2) as pct_Recuperados,
         Hospitalizados, format_number(Hospitalizados * 100 / (select sum(Hospitalizados) from ccaa_timeseries where Fecha = m.ultima_fecha), 2) as pct_Hospitalizados,
         UCI, format_number(UCI * 100 / (select sum(UCI) from ccaa_timeseries where Fecha = m.ultima_fecha), 2) as pct_UCI
  from (
    select max(Fecha) as ultima_fecha
    from ccaa_timeseries
  ) m, ccaa_timeseries ct, ccaa_iso_codes cc, ccaa_iso_codes_mapping ccm, ccaa_demography cd
  where m.ultima_fecha = ct.Fecha
    and concat("ES-", ct.CCAA) = cc.code
    and cc.code = ccm.iso_code
    and ccm.name = cd.CCAA
    and cd.Sexo = "Total"
    and cd.Periodo = "2019"
)
order by Casos desc

paragraphs.title: Coronavirus time series (data load)
paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions

val confirmedTimeseries = sc.parallelize(
    IOUtils.toString(
        new URL("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CSSEGISandData/COVID-19/master/csse_covid_19_data/csse_covid_19_time_series/time_series_covid19_confirmed_global.csv"),
        Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

val deathsTimeseries = sc.parallelize(
    IOUtils.toString(
        new URL("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CSSEGISandData/COVID-19/master/csse_covid_19_data/csse_covid_19_time_series/time_series_covid19_deaths_global.csv"),
        Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

var countryFilter = z.input("Country").toString

println("Country: " + countryFilter)
println("Raw CSV count (Confirmed): " + confirmedTimeseries.count)
println("Raw CSV count (Deaths): " + deathsTimeseries.count)

val confirmedTs = confirmedTimeseries
    .filter(_.contains(countryFilter))               // Get only a single country row
    .flatMap(s => s.split(",").drop(4).dropRight(1)) // Get all values (except for the first 4 columns (state, country, lon y lat) and the last one which is somehow failing)
    .map(s => s.toInt)                               // Convert to int
    .toDF()                                          // Convert to Dataframe
    .withColumn("id", functions.monotonically_increasing_id())  // Add an ID
    .withColumnRenamed("value", "confirmed")         // Rename the value column
        
val deathsTs = deathsTimeseries
    .filter(_.contains(countryFilter))               // Get only a single country row
    .flatMap(s => s.split(",").drop(4).dropRight(1)) // Get all values (except for the first 4 columns (state, country, lon y lat) and the last one which is somehow failing)
    .map(s => s.toInt)                               // Convert to int
    .toDF()                                          // Convert to Dataframe
    .withColumn("id", functions.monotonically_increasing_id())  // Add an ID
    .withColumnRenamed("value", "deaths")            // Rename the value column

val ts = confirmedTs
    .join(deathsTs, "id")
    .orderBy("id")

ts.show(5)

ts.registerTempTable("ts")
